[[File:Prima ZOOM logo.svg|thumb|287x287px|Stylized logo Prima ZOOM]] '''Prima ZOOM''' is a [[documentary]] [[television channel]] of FTV Prima group. Prima ZOOM was launched on 1 February 2013, complementing its sister channels [[Prima televize|Prima Family]], [[Prima Cool|Prima COOL]], and [[Prima Love]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtg.se/en/Brands--Operations/Brands/Free-TV/prima-zoom/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-12-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015110240/http://www.mtg.se/en/Brands--Operations/Brands/Free-TV/prima-zoom/ |archivedate=2014-10-15 |df= }}</ref><ref>http://zoom.iprima.cz/</ref>
Prima ZOOM's [[graphics]] identity was made by Studio Oficina, as it did also with Prima Love and Prima COOL. Its graphics and [[logo]] are based on the gesture [[Multi-touch#Multi-touch gestures|pinch-to-zoom]].<ref>http://www.ofcn.cz/project/64</ref>
Prima ZOOM [[broadcasting|broadcasts]] daily between 08.00 and 02.00. The channel is available in the [[Czech Republic|Czech]] [[Television in the Czech Republic|digital terrestrial network]] (like other channels of FTV Prima group) in [[Multiplex (television)|multiplex 3]] (like Prima Love), as well as in the basic packages of a number of [[satellite television|satellite]], [[cable television|cable]], and [[IPTV]] [[Pay television|pay-TV]] operators, and had a household penetration of well over 90% when it launched.
